00:00:00.656 --> 00:00:02.626
When I was a young officer, they told me

00:00:02.626 --> 00:00:04.894
to follow my instincts,

00:00:04.894 --> 00:00:07.150
to go with my gut,

00:00:07.150 --> 00:00:09.160
and what I've learned

00:00:09.160 --> 00:00:13.544
is that often our instincts are wrong.

00:00:13.544 --> 00:00:16.720
In the summer of 2010,

00:00:16.720 --> 00:00:20.059
there was a massive leak of classified documents

00:00:20.059 --> 00:00:23.032
that came out of the Pentagon.

00:00:23.032 --> 00:00:24.848
